  "texts": [
    "The second search using the words \"DFIG AND based AND wind AND energy AND conversion AND system AND transient AND dynamic AND analysis\" gave 24 papers that use both transient and dynamic analysis to further understand the system's response to different circumstances.",
    "These findings illustrate the increasing trend of research activities on the analysis and enhancement of DFIG systems.",
    "Fig. 12 Top 10 Countries' Scientific Production on DFIG-Based WECS Dynamic Analysis Countries' scientific production on DFIG-based WECS dynamic analysis andFigure 12 indicates the publications made by the top 10 countries.",
    "India occupies the highest number of publications more than 100, whereas China has near about 60 publications.",
    "A similar output of 25-30 publications was seen for nations such as Algeria, Morocco and Canada."
  ]
